flowchart TB
    P0["P0<br/>Production hazard<br/>auth, payments, persistence, secrets"]
    P1["P1<br/>Contract risk<br/>API, CI, deployment, dependencies"]
    P2["P2<br/>Local runtime risk<br/>source or UI behavior"]
    P3["P3<br/>Low runtime risk<br/>docs, tests, examples"]

    P0 --> P1 --> P2 --> P3

    Score["Risk score<br/>0-100"]
    Cues["Risk cues<br/>paths and added lines"]
    Gaps["Blocking gaps<br/>missing evidence"]
    Score --> P0
    Cues --> P1
    Gaps --> P0
